---

<Layout
  title="Soluciones de Software y Automatización | Desarrollo Web y Bases de Datos | Jeroo Logic"
  description="Jeroo Logic ofrece soluciones de software a medida: automatización de procesos con n8n y Make, desarrollo web, bases de datos y análisis de datos. Optimiza tu negocio con tecnología eficiente y escalable."
  image="/images/SolucionesdeSoftware-large.webp">
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-10 lg:py-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-sky-100 dark:from-sky-900 dark:to-sky-800 relative overflow-hidden" id="home">
    <div class="w-full max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="flex lg:flex-row flex-col items-center justify-between">
        <div class="flex-1 max-w-2xl lg:text-left text-center">
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-5 text-dark dark:text-light">Automatización de Procesos y Desarrollo Web con Jeroo Logic </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray dark:text-light-gray mb-8">
            Jeroo Logic desarrolla herramientas y automatizaciones escalables
            utilizando soluciones tecnológicas. Optimizamos tus procesos con
            soluciones eficientes y de bajo costo.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a href="#services" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-7 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold transition-all duration-300 border-none cursor-pointer text-base hover:bg-primary-dark hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-lg dark:bg-primary-light dark:border-2 dark:border-primary-light dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-primary-light dark:hover:text-white">Nuestros Servicios</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-transparent border-2 border-primary text-primary px-7 py-3 ml-4 rounded-full font-semibold transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer text-base hover:bg-primary hover:text-white hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-lg dark:border-primary-light dark:text-primary-light dark:hover:bg-primary-light dark:hover:text-white">Contáctanos</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center animate-float mt-12 lg:mt-0">
          <picture>
            <source
              srcset="/images/SolucionesdeSoftware-large.webp 1200w, /images/SolucionesdeSoftware-medium.webp 800w, /images/SolucionesdeSoftware-small.webp 400w"
              sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 800px"
              type="image/webp"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/SolucionesdeSoftware-large.webp"
              alt="Desarrollo de Software"
              width="800"
              height="450"
              class="max-w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-2xl"
              fetchpriority="high"
            />
          </picture>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Section -->
  <section class="py-[100px] bg-white dark:bg-dark" id="services">
    <div class="w-full max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="text-center mb-[60px]">
        <h2 class="text-4xl text-dark dark:text-light mb-4 relative inline-block">
          Nuestros Servicios
          <div class="absolute bottom-[-10px] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[200px] h-[4px] bg-primary rounded-md"></div>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray dark:text-light-gray max-w-3xl mt-5 mx-auto">
          Ofrecemos soluciones personalizadas para optimizar tus procesos
          empresariales.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-secondary rounded-[15px] p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 text-center border-t-4 border-primary hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-[#4a6fc5] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <RobotIcon class="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-4 text-dark dark:text-light">Automatizaciones</h3>
          <p class="text-gray dark:text-light-gray">
            Automatizamos tus procesos con herramientas como n8n y Make,
            reduciendo tiempos y errores.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-secondary rounded-[15px] p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 text-center border-t-4 border-primary hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-[#4a6fc5] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <DatabaseIcon class="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-4 text-dark dark:text-light">Bases de Datos</h3>
          <p class="text-gray dark:text-light-gray">
            Diseñamos e implementamos bases de datos eficientes para gestionar
            tu información crítica.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-secondary rounded-[15px] p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 text-center border-t-4 border-primary hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-[#4a6fc5] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <CloudIcon class="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-4 text-dark dark:text-light">Soluciones Cloud</h3>
          <p class="text-gray dark:text-light-gray">
            Implementamos aplicaciones escalables en la nube, en tu hosting o
            Vps .
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-secondary rounded-[15px] p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 text-center border-t-4 border-primary hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-[#4a6fc5] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <LaptopCodeIcon class="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-4 text-dark dark:text-light">Desarrollo Web</h3>
          <p class="text-gray dark:text-light-gray">
            Creación de sitios web y aplicaciones a medida con tecnologías
            modernas y flexibles.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-secondary rounded-[15px] p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 text-center border-t-4 border-primary hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-[#4a6fc5] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <SyncAltIcon class="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-4 text-dark dark:text-light">Integraciones</h3>
          <p class="text-gray dark:text-light-gray">
            Conectamos tus sistemas y aplicaciones para un flujo de trabajo
            unificado y eficiente.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-secondary rounded-[15px] p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 text-center border-t-4 border-primary hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-[#4a6fc5] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <ChartLineIcon class="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-4 text-dark dark:text-light">Análisis de Datos</h3>
          <p class="text-gray dark:text-light-gray">
            Transformamos tus datos en información valiosa para la toma de
            decisiones estratégicas.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

